data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this inviting 2-bed/3-bath unit within the coveted Liberty Park Condominium neighborhood. The master suite boasts a walk-in closet and private 3/4 bath, ensuring a serene retreat. An open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, complemented by a half-bath and garage access for effortless living. Ascend to the spacious loft, a versatile space suitable for a home office, kids' play area, or workout zone. With a brand-new roof in 2023, this home offers peace of mind. Plus, relish its prime location, mere miles from Northfield Hospital, Benedictine Assisted Living Community, Carleton College, and St. Olaf College, alongside nearby schools, restaurants, and parks. Enjoy quick access to highways 35 and 3, making this residence a gateway to all your desired destinations. Starting January 2024 the association fee will be $ 325/ monthly.
